CLI commands (UX)

eip validate <file|-> [--fix] [--format table|json]
parse + lint; optional autofix.

eip ast <file|->
print normalized AST.

eip run <file|-> --model <id> [--temp 0.2]
run a single prompt via configured adapter (stubbed).

eip harness [--models gpt4o,gemini,claude] [--temp 0.2,0.7]
execute Rosetta vectors and emit JSON reports.


